      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical used under validated installation with documented version control; FDA internal SQA procedures followed per SOP-SQA-2021-003.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented V&V pedigree. FDA CDRH maintains an institutional SQA framework covering installation qualification, version locking, and change control. All simulation scripts are version-controlled under Git tag v3.2.1. Achieved level 2 satisfies required level 2 for this medium-risk COU."
