      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and Ansys verification manual reproduced within 1% for linear static structural cases relevant to implant loading.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical has been verified against NAFEMS benchmark suite LE1 and LE10 (plate bending, stress concentration). Results reproduced within 0.4% of reference solutions. No custom solver modifications were introduced. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
